description: This file defines a React component for managing registry entries, including listing, creating, updating, and deleting registry providers. It includes UI components and uses API functions for server interactions.

methods.name: RegistryPage
methods.description: Main React component rendering the registry management page, handling state and UI for listing and managing registry providers.

methods.name: RegistryRow
methods.description: Component representing a single registry provider entry with delete functionality.

methods.name: UpsertCard
methods.description: Component providing a form to create or update registry providers.

methods.name: load
methods.description: Fetches the registry list from the server.

methods.name: save
methods.description: Saves a new or updated registry provider to the server.
